snippet.title: Castle on the Coast Trailer
snippet.description:
A hand-drawn, retro 3D collectathon. Parkour through a magic castle as George the Giraffe! String together sweet moves to explore crystal caverns, stone laden halls, and trippy alternate dimensions.

Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1341900/Castle_on_the_Coast/

Early Access on Itch.io!
https://big-heart.itch.io/castle-on-the-coast
